			INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
FROM CLI:
	Enter the links directory on the links floppy disk.
	Type INSTALL followed by a destination drive and path.
	   Any destination path name must end in a "/"
	   IE:  DH1:GAMES/
	If the links directory does not exist the install script will
	   create one for you.
	To run links just type links from the harddrive links directory.
FROM WORKBENCH:
	COPY the LINKS drawer from the links floppy disk onto your harddrive.
	OPEN the LINKS drawer on the harddrive.
	DOUBLE CLICK on the install icon.
	After the installation is finnished and no errors occurred, you may
	   delete both the INSTALL and LINKS.LZH icons from the hard drive.
	To run links just DOUBLE CLICK on the new links icon.  You will have to
	   redraw the windows or close and re-open the links drawer to see this
	   ICON.
